entry.source: {F871,1}Ah, how strong thy fist art!{F801}Asketh thou to follow me?{F801}{F802}Thou hast literally captured my{F801}heart!{F801}{F802}
entry.target: {F871,1}Ah, how strong thy fist art!{F801}Asketh thou to follow me?{F801}{F802}Thou hast literally captured my{F801}heart!{F801}{F802}

entry.source: {F871,1}The data inside thy Gauntlet?{F801}{F802}That is but a false image...{F801}What good is there in indulging in{F801}that folly?{F801}{F802}
entry.target: {F871,1}The data inside thy Gauntlet?{F801}{F802}That is but a false image...{F801}What good is there in indulging in{F801}that folly?{F801}{F802}

entry.source: {F871,1}I have memories, too. Memories of{F801}when a human and I fought together{F801}as allies...{F801}{F802}Wouldst thou bring back these{F801}memories of those nostalgic times?{F801}{F802}
entry.target: {F871,1}I have memories, too. Memories of{F801}when a human and I fought together{F801}as allies...{F801}{F802}Wouldst thou bring back these{F801}memories of those nostalgic times?{F801}{F802}

entry.source: {F871,1}Thy happiness liveth in the past.{F801}Those who cannot take pleasure from{F801}the present must die.{F801}{F802}
entry.target: {F871,1}Thy happiness liveth in the past.{F801}Those who cannot take pleasure from{F801}the present must die.{F801}{F802}

entry.source: {F871,1}"A long journey."{F801}"A brief moment."{F801}"I don't know."{F801}{F802}
entry.target: {F871,1}"A long journey."{F801}"A brief moment."{F801}"I don't know."{F801}{F802}

entry.source: {F871,1}Then think of meeting me as a fork{F801}in thy road.{F801}{F802}Will thy journey come to an end?{F801}Or shall thee gain a new ally?{F801}Choose wisely.{F801}{F802}
entry.target: {F871,1}Then think of meeting me as a fork{F801}in thy road.{F801}{F802}Will thy journey come to an end?{F801}Or shall thee gain a new ally?{F801}Choose wisely.{F801}{F802}

entry.source: {F871,1}A journey? How foolish. Life should{F801}be treated as running about freely.{F801}{F802}I shall show thee that even life and{F801}death are within thy grasp.{F801}{F802}
entry.target: {F871,1}A journey? How foolish. Life should{F801}be treated as running about freely.{F801}{F802}I shall show thee that even life and{F801}death are within thy grasp.{F801}{F802}

entry.source: {F871,1}A long journey? What about those{F801}whose lives are short journeys?{F801}{F802}Thou dost not see that there are{F801}others, who do not get to experience{F801}as much as thou hast in life.{F801}{F802}
entry.target: {F871,1}A long journey? What about those{F801}whose lives are short journeys?{F801}{F802}Thou dost not see that there are{F801}others, who do not get to experience{F801}as much as thou hast in life.{F801}{F802}

entry.source: {F871,1}Souls are eternal... This life is{F801}but a blink of an eye in comparison.{F801}{F802}
entry.target: {F871,1}Souls are eternal... This life is{F801}but a blink of an eye in comparison.{F801}{F802}

entry.source: {F871,1}Then can I end thy brief moment?{F801}{F802}
entry.target: {F871,1}Then can I end thy brief moment?{F801}{F802}

entry.source: {F871,1}I lack an answer as well.{F801}{F802}...Perhaps it is the search for an{F801}answer that gives our lives meaning.{F801}{F802}
entry.target: {F871,1}I lack an answer as well.{F801}{F802}...Perhaps it is the search for an{F801}answer that gives our lives meaning.{F801}{F802}

entry.source: {F871,1}Thou hast not lived long enough to{F801}be able to say that...{F801}{F802}
entry.target: {F871,1}Thou hast not lived long enough to{F801}be able to say that...{F801}{F802}

entry.source: {F871,1}I wish to return home.{F801}What dost thou think?{F801}{F802}
entry.target: {F871,1}I wish to return home.{F801}What dost thou think?{F801}{F802}

entry.source: {F871,1}You would dare order me around!?{F801}Nay, sir, I will stay right here!{F801}{F802}
entry.target: {F871,1}You would dare order me around!?{F801}Nay, sir, I will stay right here!{F801}{F802}

entry.source: {F871,1}Would it not be proper manners to{F801}escort me there?{F801}{F802}I shall remain in thy stock until{F801}I have reached my home.{F801}{F802}
entry.target: {F871,1}Would it not be proper manners to{F801}escort me there?{F801}{F802}I shall remain in thy stock until{F801}I have reached my home.{F801}{F802}

entry.source: {F871,1}You would try to convince me to leave{F801}my companions in battle? That shall{F801}not happen.{F801}{F802}
entry.target: {F871,1}You would try to convince me to leave{F801}my companions in battle? That shall{F801}not happen.{F801}{F802}

entry.source: {F871,1}When thou sayest that... For some{F801}reason, I feel the urge to stay.{F801}{F802}
entry.target: {F871,1}When thou sayest that... For some{F801}reason, I feel the urge to stay.{F801}{F802}

entry.source: {F871,1}Of course I shan't be leaving right{F801}now.{F801}{F802}I must first kill thee.{F801}{F802}
entry.target: {F871,1}Of course I shan't be leaving right{F801}now.{F801}{F802}I must first kill thee.{F801}{F802}

entry.source: {F871,1}Samurai, let us drink together and{F801}make merry.{F801}{F802}...Now, drink.{F801}{F802}
entry.target: {F871,1}Samurai, let us drink together and{F801}make merry.{F801}{F802}...Now, drink.{F801}{F802}

entry.source: {F871,1}"I can't drink that."{F801}"I don't drink that."{F801}"I won't drink that."{F801}{F802}
entry.target: {F871,1}"I can't drink that."{F801}"I don't drink that."{F801}"I won't drink that."{F801}{F802}
